#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Little_Spider, race=AE_ext_monsters_monster
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Little_Spider.cfg:4
msgid "Little Spider"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Little_Spider, race=AE_ext_monsters_monster
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Little_Spider.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Little Spiders are said to roam the depths of Knalga, devouring many victims."
" They have a vicious bite and can also fling webs through the air to trap "
"their prey."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Mother_Mudcrawler, race=AE_ext_monsters_monster
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Mother_Mudcrawler.cfg:4
msgid "Mother Mudcrawler"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Mother_Mudcrawler, race=AE_ext_monsters_monster
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Mother_Mudcrawler.cfg:35
msgid ""
"Giant Mudcrawlers are a larger kind of Mudcrawler, and are magical constructs"
" of soil and water. They attack by belching lumps of mud at their foes, or by"
" striking them with their fists."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Scylla, race=AE_ext_monsters_seacreatures
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Scylla.cfg:4
msgid "Scylla"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_monsters_Scylla, race=AE_ext_monsters_seacreatures
#: .\units\EE_units\monsters\Scylla.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Scholars differ as to the ancestry of the Triple Head Hydra. Some hold that "
"they are the immature young, or mature cousins, of One Head Hydra. Others "
"hold them up as a primitive offshoot of the Nagas. What is certain is that it"
" is wise to avoid waters where they are known to congregate."
msgstr ""

